00:20:08,780 --> 00:20:10,340
So it looks like you need to take a look

466
00:20:10,340 --> 00:20:12,940
at what's happening in your resume review stage, huh?

467
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:14,940
At the phone screen stage,

468
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:18,380
you have many more men than women, 15 and 10 respectively,

469
00:20:18,380 --> 00:20:19,900
but they make it through at the same rate.

470
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:24,900
So that stack, that frame seems to be okay.

471
00:20:25,860 --> 00:20:26,700
Then for the onsite,

472
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:28,900
you have 80% of men making it through,

